The lawyer carries an axe to court?
The news was really exciting at first glance, and it also exploded in the legal circle.
Quanzhou City, Fujian Zhongfa subsequently fined the lawyers involved 500 yuan, and suggested in writing that Quanzhou City Bar Association investigate and deal with it.
According to the Beijing News, a few days ago, the Quanzhou City Law Association issued a formal notice saying that the behavior of the two lawyers does not involve illegal violations and is not punished according to law.
From many reports, Quanzhou City Law Association's treatment is not to protect the short or engage in confrontation, but has been recognized by Quanzhou Intermediate People's Court.
An incident that might have caused tension within the legal community was finally properly resolved.
The reversal of the matter stems from a more complete restoration of the truth: the axe carried by the lawyer involved is the same style and the same model as the defendant's murder weapon, but it has not been opened. It is only used as auxiliary evidence in the evidence cross-examination link, and there is no subjective intention to intimidate or "endanger the safety of the court."
Judging whether the behavior of the lawyers involved is illegal and illegal, there are four very important details that need to be paid attention to: First, the local court has only presented the axe photos twice before the court session. From the perspective of defense, it is necessary to show the original axe; second, the axe is purchased only one hour before the court session, not the lawyer does not want to seek the judge's consent, but objectively failed to contact the judge; third, the entire axe has not been used or improperly.
Combined with these circumstances, it can be seen that the lawyers involved "appear in court with axes" have nothing to do with evil, just to defend.
After clarifying the whole fact, Quanzhou City Law Association did not push the boat, but resisted the pressure to make a decision not to punish.
And this decision, also can withstand the test of facts and laws.
As for bringing the axe as a controlled knife to the court without the permission of the court, it is really easy to cause uneasiness and misunderstanding.
Due to safety and caution, Quanzhou Intermediate People's Court's previous fines and judicial recommendations are also understandable.
In order to maintain the dignity of lawyers and prevent individual courts from making it difficult for lawyers, the Supreme Law issued the "Rules for the Safety Inspection of the Judicial Police of the People's Court" in 2014, establishing the principle that lawyers do not need to conduct personal safety inspections when they appear in court.
Since the release of the rule, the majority of lawyers have led by example, and there are few incidents that endanger the safety of the court due to security loopholes.
In a very few cases like Quanzhou, as long as the spirit of mutual respect and understanding is communicated, misunderstanding is not difficult to eliminate.
As a self-regulatory organization of the lawyer industry, the Bar Association undertakes the dual mission of punishing illegal and safeguarding legal.
In the past, individual law associations have been criticized for focusing on punishment and losing their protection.
The decision of Quanzhou Law Association, both in terms of process and results, is commendable and sets an example for more law associations to perform their duties correctly.
From October 1st, which tax benefits will affect our purse?
Xinhua News Agency, Shanghai, October 1 (Reporter Sang Wei) The new personal income tax law will be implemented on January 1, 2019. In order to allow the broad masses of the people to enjoy the tax reduction dividends as soon as possible, from October 1st, the actual income of taxpayers will be deducted according to the threshold of 5,000 yuan per month, and the new tax rate table will be applied.
With the landing of the New Deal, what benefits will affect the purse strings of the masses?
Good one: The tax reduction of wages and salaries is obvious
Taxpayers who obtain wages and salaries after October 1 can deduct the basic deduction cost of 5,000 yuan / month and apply the new tax rate scale. Most taxpayers have different degrees of tax reduction, especially the tax reduction for middle and low income earners is more obvious.
According to the tax reduction table of different income groups, the monthly income after deducting the "three risks and one gold" is 8000 yuan, 10000 yuan, 20000 yuan, and 50000 yuan. The tax payable after the tax reform is 90 yuan, 290 yuan, 1590 yuan, 9090 yuan, compared with the monthly threshold of 3500 yuan, the corresponding tax reduction ratio is 73.9%, 61.1%, 49.8%, 18.8%.
It is worth noting that due to holiday reasons, the wages that should be paid in October by various units at the end of September may be applied to the new basic deduction fee and tax rate.
To this end, the withholding client software used by the tax department has provided the corresponding tax calculation function, but the corresponding tax still needs to be declared and paid during the statutory declaration period.
Good 2: Low tax rate range is significantly enlarged
In addition to raising the threshold, the new tax rate will be applied from October 1st.
The seven-grade tax rate of this salary and salary income is the same as before, and there is no change, but the tax rate has changed significantly. The 3%, 10%, and 20% of the three-grade low tax rate has expanded significantly, and the 25% tax rate has narrowed, while the 30%, 35%, and 45% of the three higher tax rates remain unchanged.
It is worth noting that the tax law has also adjusted the tax rates of various grades of production and operation income, and the lower limit of the most high-end 35% tax rate has been raised from 100,000 yuan to 500,000 yuan.
This means that individual industrial and commercial households and sole proprietorship partnerships will benefit from tax reform.
"From the early calculation of individual tax cuts for Shanghai taxpayers, the majority of taxpayers will fully feel the dividends of tax reform, especially for low- and middle-income people."
Lan Min, head of the personal income tax department of the Shanghai Municipal Taxation Bureau of the State Administration of Taxation, said.
Good 3: Tax service is more convenient and optimized
Since the publication of the new personal income tax law, the Shanghai tax department has carried out a series of comprehensive and extensive tax publicity actions.
On the one hand, the key tax sources, key enterprises to carry out "one-to-one, point-to-point" policy guidance.
Pudong New Area Taxation Bureau has visited Apple Trade (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Alipay (China) Network Technology Co., Ltd., Red Star Macalline Home Group Co., Ltd. and other large enterprises. These enterprises have a large number of employees, a large amount of withholding work, a large amount of tax payment, and the tax department has taken the initiative to guide and answer questions; Xuhui District Taxation Bureau visited the large-scale labor enterprises in the region, such as Zhongzhi Financial Consulting Co., Ltd., Zhongzhi Shanghai Economic and Technical Cooperation Company, etc., etc., timely collect business concerns, respond to solve problems, etc.
On the other hand, for the general public taxpayers, carry out "all-round, multi-dimensional, three-dimensional" tax policy push.
The use of Shanghai tax official website, WeChat public number, microblogging and other channels to push policy hotspots in a timely manner to ensure that policy publicity is in place.
At the same time, from September 28th, the Shanghai Tax WeChat public number went online 12366 intelligent consultation platform, and through the "artificial + intelligent" tax service consultation, carried out the "targeted" intelligent integration tax reform publicity service.
