According to the data, the consumption potential of rural residents continued to be released. In the first half of this year, the retail sales of rural consumer goods increased by 10.5%, which was 1.3 percentage points higher than that of cities and towns.
Visiting a poor village in a western county, there is only one convenience store in the village, and some goods are familiar with the store. "Goldfish" is marked as "Golden Dragon Oil," and "Wangzi" has become "Wangzi," "Shanzhai" has many goods.
Over the years, similar phenomena have frequently been exposed. Some rural fake and shoddy goods are famous brands, with similar names, similar packaging, and fake and true, which is too much to prevent.
